						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone set up against the front wall of the temple of Kallēśvara.</hi></p>						

						<p>Siṁghaṇa—A.D. 1246.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in the <hi rend="bold">38th year</hi> of the reign of <hi rend="bold">Siṁhadēva, Parābhava, Mārgaśira śu. Daśami, Sunday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1246, November 18.</hi> The <hi rend="italic">tithi,</hi> however, commenced after ·19 on Mond the 19th.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of a hero in a fight. <hi rend="bold">Rāya-Rāhuta Khaṇḍeya</hi> and <hi rend="bold">Kēśava-Rāhuta</hi> are mentioned.</p>						

						</summary>
